commit.message:
Remove chorus.h files from i386, rs6000 and sparc config directories.

Add config/chorus.h instead.

From-SVN: r44538

+	config directories.  Add config/chorus.h instead.
+

         * POTFILES.in: Add ssa-ccp.c
